name: GN
description:
GN

This is an illustration series dedicated to amazing thread, started by 6529 on twitter that serves as NFT slang explanation for newcomers, as well as a collective item for those who know the way

quote from @punk6529 aka 6529: "gn means "good night"

We say good night to each other because we are a friendly happy optimistic global community and it is nice to say good night to your friends as you end your day 

(20 hours after you say gm and 4 hours before you say gm again)"
